    ↓
Response Generator

That is VERY close to modern AI startups.

MOST Important Insight

AI systems are NOT just:

LLM API calls

The REAL backend is:

orchestration
tools
memory
workflow control

That is what creates:

AI agents
AI assistants
AI operating environments
